lyTime":"2019-09-02T16:34:44.000Z","msg":"但中共既制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:35:54.000Z","msg":"老公同仔可能比中共控制住，而家裡外不是人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2685d2f69b2b354cbf6017ae73607b63358b248e","tid":1533124,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:36:11.000Z","msg":"[澄清]國難五金課金問題&mdash;照舊課！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1</a><br />\n <br />\n國難五金專訪 [國難老闆同一眾員工已保釋,開鋪事直請留意國難五金FB]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521301/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521301/page/1</a><br />\n <br />\n【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a><br />\n <br />\nFB: 國難五金, 香港自由之書<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4e48235035bf98ca7a93d5b956860ab877055b1","tid":1533124,"uid":271617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:36:38.000Z","msg":"其實林鄭可直接答應五大訴求，之後向傳媒講自已已向中央請辭。<br />\n1. 中央因林鄭自己下台（中共有下台階）<br />\n2. 林鄭向傳媒講自已已向中央請辭 （中共冇得反對，因為中共之前講過高度自治）<br />\n3. 林鄭可以番英國 （唔會因美國人權法而被制裁）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}